org.jboss.windup.exec.configuration.options

Class UserRulesDirectoryOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jboss.windup.config.AbstractConfigurationOption
      • org.jboss.windup.config.AbstractPathConfigurationOption
        • org.jboss.windup.exec.configuration.options.UserRulesDirectoryOption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationOption

    public class UserRulesDirectoryOption
extends AbstractPathConfigurationOption
    Indicates the directory or directories that will contain rules provided by the user. Multiple paths can be specified separated by a space (for example, --userRulesDirectory PATH_1 PATH_2).
    Author:
    Jesse Sightler
